<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Affidavit</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #0056b3;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .content {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .form-field {
            margin: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            min-width: 150px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .field-value {
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #000;
            min-height: 20px;
            padding: 2px 5px;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding-top: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .italic {
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .center {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>AFFIDAVIT</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I, <span class="bold">{{ deponent_name | default('[Deponent Name]') }}</span>, son/daughter of <span class="bold">{{ father_name | default('[Father\'s Name]') }}</span>, aged about <span class="bold">{{ age | default('[Your Age]') }}</span> years, residing at <span class="bold">{{ deponent_address | default('[Your Complete Address]') }}</span>, by occupation <span class="bold">{{ occupation | default('[Your Occupation]') }}</span>, do hereby solemnly affirm and declare as under:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Deponent Details:</div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Name:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_name | default('[Your Full Name]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Father's Name:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ father_name | default('[Father\'s Name]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Age:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ age | default('[Your Age]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Occupation:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ occupation | default('[Your Occupation]') }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
                <div class="field-label">Address:</div>
                <div class="field-value">{{ deponent_address | default('[Your Complete Address]') }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Statement of Facts:</div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>{{ statement_of_facts | default('1. That I am the deponent of this affidavit and I have personal knowledge of the facts stated herein.\n\n2. That [state the relevant facts and circumstances that form the basis of this affidavit].\n\n3. That [continue with additional facts as necessary].\n\n4. That the facts stated above are true to the best of my knowledge and belief.') | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I state that the facts mentioned above are true and correct to the best of my knowledge and belief, and nothing material has been concealed therefrom.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Solemnly affirmed and declared this <span class="bold">{{ current_date }}</span> at <span class="bold">{{ place | default('[Your City]') }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <p>DEPONENT</p>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <p>(<span class="bold">{{ deponent_name | default('[Your Name]') }}</span>)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Note: This is a draft affidavit. It should be reviewed and attested by a Notary Public or Oath Commissioner.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
